### 1. Login as Warehouse staff
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "warehouse@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Save token from response
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 2. Get pending export orders
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/orders/pending-export?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get order detail
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Export for sale (with GHN creation)
### IMPORTANT: Không cần gửi "createdBy" - Backend tự động lấy từ token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/export-for-sale
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "reason": "Xuất kho bán hàng - Giao cho khách",
  "note": "Kiểm tra kỹ trước khi giao",
  "items": [
    {
      "productSku": "IP15PM-256-BLK",
      "serialNumbers": [
        "IP15PM256BLK001"
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### 5. Check export order detail
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/export-orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Check order GHN info
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Get GHN tracking
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/ghn-tracking
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Export for warranty
POST http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/export-for-warranty
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "orderId": 2,
  "reason": "Xuất kho bảo hành - Sản phẩm lỗi",
  "note": "Màn hình bị vỡ",
  "productSku": "IP15PM-256-BLK",
  "serialNumber": "IP15PM256BLK002"
}

### 9. Get all export orders
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/export-orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Get export orders by status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/export-orders?status=COMPLETED
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
